title: Businessweek Extra- Daniel Boulud
itunes:title: Businessweek Extra- Daniel Boulud
description:
Featuring a conversation with Chef and Restaurateur Daniel Boulud. He discusses offering his kitchen's menu in a terrace setting. Boulud also walks through the outlook for restaurants.

Hosts: Carol Massar and Jason Kelly. Producer: Doni Holloway.
